# 5 Ways to Fix T&E Managers’ Pain Points
Road blocks are a natural part of any travel and expense program, but some tools and strategies can help. Start here.

Feel like you’re always running into obstacles with your T&E program? You’re not alone. The daily grind of keeping travelers happy, monitoring spend, and maintaining compliance can feel like a constant barrage of pinpricks.

Navan has your back with this guide. Download it to learn:
* 5 painful issues for teams managing T&E programs
* Why these obstacles can be particularly difficult to overcome
* Solutions for easing — or even eliminating — the pain

